    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Three or four hundred members\nOf the Industrial Workers of the\nWorld not yet in the city prison\ntoday entered on starvation\nstrike\" in sympathy with their\nbrothers confined in jail for speak\ning on the street.\n\n\nThis step was taken because of\nthe announcement of Chief of Po-\nlice Sullivan that common Grimm\nais in the city Jail were to be fed\nturkey while the men who volun-\ntarily went to Jail in defense of the\nright of free speech are to be given\nThanksgiving diet of bread and\nwater."
    }
  ]
